OL,5,EHOMELESSNESS IS CRIMINAL? Qjj  
OL,7,BReducing homelessness could help       
OL,8,BreduceEcrime and re-offending,Bsays a  
OL,9,Bnew report.                            
OL,11,BYoung people are particularly at risk  
OL,12,Bof turning toEcriminal behaviourBif    
OL,13,Bthey don't have a home of their own.   
OL,15,BThe National Association for the Care  
OL,16,Band Resettlement of Offenders report,  
OL,17,EGoing Straight Home,Breveals that 25%  
OL,18,Bof young prisoners were homeless before
OL,19,Bbeing imprisoned.EClub investigates... 
