OL,5,EHOMELESSNESS IS CRIMINAL? Qjj  
OL,7,BAnother problem for young offenders who
OL,8,Bfind themselves homeless on release    
OL,9,Bfrom prison is the stigma which hinders
OL,10,Bany chance ofEstarting afresh.         
OL,12,B"It's hard for young offenders to get  
OL,13,Etraining and jobsBwithout the added    
OL,14,Bproblem of not having a permanent      
OL,15,Baddress," says NACRO's Paul Cavadino.  
OL,17,B"With that added pressure, it's even   
OL,18,Eharder to resist returning to crimeBto 
OL,19,Bsurvive," he adds.                     
