OL,5,EHOMELESSNESS IS CRIMINAL? Qjj  
OL,7,BWhat can be done to stop this link     
OL,8,BbetweenEhomelessness and crime,        
OL,9,Bparticularly among teenagers?          
OL,11,B"There needs to be more support for    
OL,12,Byoung adults leaving local authority   
OL,13,Bcare," says Paul Cavadino of NACRO.    
OL,15,B"Benefit cuts haven't helped and if    
OL,16,Bpeople can't live independently it can 
OL,17,Bonly increase the temptation to steal, 
OL,18,Bor turning toEprostitution,Bto live."  
