OL,5,EHOMELESSNESS IS CRIMINAL? Qjj  
OL,7,EPrince CharlesBbumped into an old      
OL,8,Bschool friend of his who works at the  
OL,9,EBig IssueBoffice - a reminder that     
OL,10,Bhomelessness can happen to anyone.     
OL,12,B"Even with a supportive home background
OL,13,Byoung people today can find it hard to 
OL,14,Bmaintain theirEself-confidenceBagainst 
OL,15,Bthe pressure of modern life.           
OL,17,B"A person's identity is determined so  
OL,18,Boften only byEthe money they earn,"Bhe 
OL,19,Bwrites in the new Big Issue magazine.  
