OL,5,EHOMELESSNESS IS CRIMINAL? Qjj  
OL,7,BNACRO argue the following policy       
OL,8,Bchanges would help reduce homelessness 
OL,9,Band crime among teenagers.             
OL,11,EBRestoring income support for 16-17   
OL,12,  Byear olds.                           
OL,13,EBReviewing help given to care leavers 
OL,14,  Bto find somewhere to live.           
OL,15,EBProviding help in prisons to enable  
OL,16,  Boffenders to keep existing homes.    
OL,17,EBReinstating prisoners' eligibility   
OL,18,  Bto claim housing benefit to keep     
OL,19,  Btheir accommodation for up to a year.
